thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Sheila Zielke

author: Sheila Zielke
title: Sheila Zielke
text: 100% satisfied!! My daughters dress was exactly what she wanted after viewing pictures on website. The color, size & awesome quality. Couldn't believe how fast it had shipped, too. Ordered the dress on a Thursday & received it on the following Monday. Would totally recommend this website!!
